div.welcome-mat
  h1.welcome-heading Talkin' Trash
  h2.welcome-sub-heading People are always talking, maybe even about you!
  img(src="images/pngguru.com.png" class="welcome-img" alt="cartoon racoon")
  a(href="/users/signup" class="welcome-button") Sign Up
div.container.mb-3
  div.row.mt-3
    div.col-md.mb-3
      h2.sub-heading Talk Trash
      p.trio-content Everyone loves talking about other people! Its always better when you can do it without the reprecussions of seeing them face to face.
    div.col-md.mb-3
      h2.sub-heading Membership
      p.trio-content You are able to upgrade your membership to see who is posting and when. What good is silly fun without paywalls to alienate users and make others feel superior?
    div.col-md.mb-3
      h2.sub-heading Have Fun
      p.trio-content This website is intended to be good fun! We understand feelings can get hurt from time to time but the best way to get over hurt feelings is to lash out and hurt other people's feelings!
  h1.main-heading.mt-3 Here's what some members have been saying!
  div.post-box.mt-3
    each post in smallPosts
      div.post-card
        div.post-header
          h1.post-title.mb-1= post.title
          h3.post-author Posted by ???? on ????
        div.post-body
          p.post-content= post.content
  div.mt-5.mb-5.center-content
    h1.sub-heading Become a part of something and start talkin' some trash!
    a(href="/users/signup" class="btn btn-primary p-3") Sign Up
